      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Recevez, Monsieur, l'assurance de ma considération distinguée. ¶ Universal Exhibition of 1867, Paris ¶ General Commission, Group IX, Class 88 ¶ Imperial Commission. ¶ Paris, 31 October 1867...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">67.10.31</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From F. Le Play</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">RB MSS M197, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens, Melbourne.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letterhead of the Commission Impériale.</p>
               </note>
               <seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">EXPOSITION UNIVERSELLE</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">DE 1867</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">A PARIS.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">COMMISARIAT GÉNÉRAL.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">Groupe IX.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">Classe</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>88.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">COMMISSION IMPÉRIALE.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">Paris, le 31 octobre 1867.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">Monsieur,</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>J'ai l'honneur de vous adresser le Diplôme de la</seg>
               <seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>médaille d'argent<seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">qui vous a été décernée.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Je joins à ce Diplôme le relevé des prix et mentions qui vous ont été attribués dans les concours partiels ouverts du 1er avril au 31 octobre, et qui ont motivé la décision définitive du Jury international.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Un premier prix:</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Balantium antarcticum.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Corrected by hand from ‘antarticum’.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Recevez, Monsieur, l'assurance de ma considération distinguée.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">Le Conseiller d'Etat, Commissaire général,</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>F Le Play</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">M. F. Muller,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">à Melbourne. (Australie.)</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Universal Exhibition of 1867, Paris</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">General Commission, Group IX, Class 88</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">Imperial Commission.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Paris, 31 October 1867</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honour to send you the Diploma for the silver medal that has been awarded to you.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See Exposition Universelle, Paris to M, 31 October 1867 (in this edition as 67-10-31a).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I enclose with this Diploma the statement of prizes and honours conferred on you during the partial exhibitions open from 1 April to 31 October, which have been the basis of the definitive decision by the international jury.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>A first prize:</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Balantium antarcticum</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Be assured, Sir, of my highest esteem</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">F. Le Play</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Counsellor of State, Commissioner General</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Mr F. Muller,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(Australia.)</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plantnames"
               style="font-style: italic; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Balantium antarcticum</p>
         </div>
      </body>
   </text>
